.Dd $Mdocdate: May 18 2009 $
.Dt UDL 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm udl
.Nd DisplayLink DL-120 / DL-160 USB display devices
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "udl* at uhub?"
.Cd "wsdisplay* at udl?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver supports USB display devices based on the DisplayLink DL-120 / DL-160
graphic chip.
.Sh HARDWARE
The following devices should work:
.Pp
.Bl -tag -width Ds -offset indent -compact
.It Century Corp. Japan Plus One LCD-8000U
.It DisplayLink USB<->DVI Adapter
.It König CMP-USBVGA10
.It ForwardVideo EasyCAP008 USB to DVI
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr usb 4 ,
.Xr wscons 4 ,
.Xr wsdisplay 4
